 SQL Server Index and Statistics Maintenance 

 IndexOptimize is the SQL Server Maintenance Solutionâ€™s stored procedure for rebuilding and reorganizing indexes and updating statistics. IndexOptimize is supported on SQL Server 2005, SQL Server 2008, SQL Server 2008 R2, SQL Server 2012, SQL Server 2014, SQL Server 2016, and SQL Server 2017. 

 
 Download 

 Download  MaintenanceSolution.sql . This script creates all the objects and jobs that you need. You can also  download  the objects as separate scripts. 

 
